{"tid":785544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"籃波撚係咪都有拎白卡？","createTime":"2018-08-19T09:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T10:14:15.000Z","uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7b0db13b4ceb14847e8637fb1285c39b0526c8","tid":785544,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的 啱啱去gym room操野 喺free weight area (有啲似我上個post 係同一條友嚟）<br />\n有條友一個人霸咗三對dumbbell 有個師兄話完佢<br />\n不過佢口疾疾 自己都唔知自己講緊乜 <br />\n個師兄知佢個腦有事都無再理佢<br />\n<br />\n咁啱條友就拎咗我要個對啞鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  算啦 好好地問佢應該都ok<br />\n「師兄 呢對啞鈴仲用唔用 借嚟用一組得唔得？」<br />\n「等陣」 講完呢句 佢就將對啞鈴放返落架 之後除咗個耳機問我咩事<br />\n我真係屌你個老母係咪弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n「無 我諗住借你個對啞鈴用 你係咪唔用？」<br />\n「唔用...依家唔用住」<br />\n<br />\n我真係打咗個突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野依家唔用住？<br />\n用就用 唔用就唔用 你依家唔用住係咪即係等陣我用完要俾返你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511d0e5c3e9bd7530978b041d5f75b7bca9ca0d6","tid":785544,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"上個post<br />\n<br />\n籃波撚可唔可以鳩少陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/785512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/785512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"101cb49ae6170c9274f23b6eb2bbd578c6ef3300","tid":785544,"uid":143481,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"先唔講你幾撚小氣住<br />\n想問下你講既故事同籃球同白卡有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到1999"},{"pid":"016d8be93b8450ff5eae894c05d3bfb306bf08dd","tid":785544,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"101cb49ae6170c9274f23b6eb2bbd578c6ef3300","tid":785544,"uid